<Defs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../../Schemas/MutationDef.xsd">
	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef Name ="UngulateJawPart" ParentName="AnimalJawPart" Abstract="true">
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>

	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef Name ="UngulateEarPart" ParentName="AnimalEarPart" Abstract="true">
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>

	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef Name ="UngulateTailPart" ParentName="AnimalTailPart" Abstract="true">
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>

	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef ParentName="PawnmorphPart">
		<defName>EtherHoofHand</defName>
		<label>hoof</label>
		<description>It's terrifying, but [PAWN_nameDef]'s hands are nothing more than hooves now. Holding things, grabbing things and doing anything requiring thumbs is going to be a lot more difficult.</description>
		<parts>
			<li>Hand</li>
		</parts>
		<mutationMemory>EtherHoofHand</mutationMemory>
		<classInfluence>Ungulate</classInfluence>
		<mutationTale>HandsBecomeHooves</mutationTale>
		<stages>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>-1</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.8</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<labelOverride>mishappen hoof</labelOverride>
				<description>This entire hand has melded together in a grotesque fashion, causing it to look like a malformed hoof.</description>
				<stopChance>0.3</stopChance>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>-0.5</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.2</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<labelOverride>clumsy nails</labelOverride>
				<description>The fingernails on this hand have broadened and thickened to a point where they're much harder to use, and they get in the way contstantly.</description>
				<stopChance>0.3</stopChance>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>0</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<labelOverride>thick nails</labelOverride>
				<description>Each finger on this hand is tipped with a thicker nail that's slowly dominating the length of each digit.</description>
				<stopChance>0.3</stopChance>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.2</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-.1</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<labelOverride>hoof-fingers</labelOverride>
				<description>Each finger on this hand has a large, dark hoof-like nail on it. Some of the fingers seem to be shortening.</description>
				<stopChance>0.3</stopChance>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.4</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.20</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<description>Above a humanlike palm, two fingers have paired up and merged. This reduces manipulation, but not nearly as much as having a full hoof instead.</description>
				<labelOverride>handhoof</labelOverride>
				<stopChance>0.3</stopChance>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.6</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.40</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<description>This hand, or hoof, is quickly becoming less flexible and more like a regular hoof. Its usability may be hampered soon.</description>
				<labelOverride>inflexible handhoof</labelOverride>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.8</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.6</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<label>unfamiliar</label>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.99</minSeverity>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.2</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<description>[PAWN_nameDef] has adapted to using hooves, and will have slightly less trouble with working with them.</description>
				<label>adapted</label>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>1.5</minSeverity>
				<!-- adaption cream -->
				<!-- only pawns with the Paragon aspect or adaption cream can get this stage -->
				<labelOverride>handhoof</labelOverride>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>-0.1</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<description>Further adaptation has resulted in the hoof splitting apart and growing into two hoof-tipped fingers and a thumb.  They look strange, but they give [PAWN_nameDef] better manipulation than a regular hoof would.</description>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>2.5</minSeverity>
				<!-- only pawns with the Paragon aspect can get this stage -->
				<labelOverride>dextrous handhoof</labelOverride>
				<partEfficiencyOffset>0</partEfficiencyOffset>
				<description>Even further adaptation to this handhoof has increased the flexibility of the hoof-fingers to the point where they function about as well as an ordinary hand.</description>
			</li>
		</stages>
		<comps>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.CompProperties_MutationSeverityAdjust">
				<severityPerDay>0.15</severityPerDay>
			</li>
		</comps>
		<categories>
			<li>Extreme</li>
		</categories>
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>

	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef ParentName="PawnmorphPart">
		<defName>EtherUnguligradeLeg</defName>
		<label>unguligrade</label>
		<description>The shape of [PAWN_nameDef]'s legs reminds one more of a beast than a human, for they now stand on their toes instead of their heel, which has elongated. This does, however, put a spring in their step.</description>
		<parts>
			<li>Leg</li>
		</parts>
		<classInfluence>Ungulate</classInfluence>
		<mutationTale>LegBecameDigitgrade</mutationTale>
		<stages>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>crooked</labelOverride>
				<description>[PAWN_nameDef]'s leg seems to have degraded into something that looks awfully uncomfortable to walk on.</description>
				<minSeverity>-1</minSeverity>
				<capMods>
					<li>
						<capacity>Moving</capacity>
						<offset>-0.4</offset>
					</li>
				</capMods>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>readjusting</labelOverride>
				<description>The bones in [PAWN_nameDef]'s leg are growing longer or shorter as need be. It will be rather difficult and painful to move while this change is taking place.</description>
				<minSeverity>0</minSeverity>
				<capMods>
					<li>
						<capacity>Moving</capacity>
						<offset>-0.3</offset>
					</li>
				</capMods>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<label>unfamiliar</label>
				<minSeverity>0.3</minSeverity>
				<description>The shape of [PAWN_nameDef]'s legs reminds one more of a beast than a human, for they now stand on their toes instead of their heel, which has elongated. They'll need some time to get used to the new shape.</description>
				<capMods>
					<li>
						<capacity>Moving</capacity>
						<offset>-0.1</offset>
					</li>
				</capMods>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>1</minSeverity>
				<label>adapted</label>
				<capMods>
					<li>
						<capacity>Moving</capacity>
						<offset>0.1</offset>
					</li>
				</capMods>
			</li>
		</stages>
		<comps>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.CompProperties_MutationSeverityAdjust">
				<severityPerDay>0.25</severityPerDay>
			</li>
		</comps>
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>

	<Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef ParentName="PawnmorphSkinPart">
		<defName>EtherHideLimb</defName>
		<label>hide</label>
		<description>A thick leathery hide has formed over this limb, adding some natural defense.</description>
		<parts>
			<li>Torso</li>
			<li>Head</li>
			<li>Ear</li>
			<li>Arm</li>
			<li>Hand</li>
			<li>Leg</li>
			<li>Foot</li>
			<li>Tail</li>
			<li>MorphTail</li>
		</parts>
		<categories>
			<li>Minor</li>
		</categories>
		<classInfluence>Ungulate</classInfluence>
		<mutationLogRulePack>HideGrowthLogPack</mutationLogRulePack>
		<stages>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>thick skin</labelOverride>
				<description>The skin on this limb seems to be slightly more tough than the average human.</description>
				<minSeverity>0</minSeverity>
				<statOffsets>
					<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.01</ArmorRating_Sharp>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>hard skin</labelOverride>
				<minSeverity>0.2</minSeverity>
				<description>The skin on this limb seems to be quite a bit tougher than the average human.</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.01</ArmorRating_Blunt>
					<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.01</ArmorRating_Sharp>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>bristly skin</labelOverride>
				<description>Rough, thick bristles have sprouted from this limb as the skin grows thicker.</description>
				<minSeverity>0.4</minSeverity>
				<statOffsets>
					<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.01</ArmorRating_Blunt>
					<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.02</ArmorRating_Sharp>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<labelOverride>leathery skin</labelOverride>
				<description>The skin on this limb is greatly thicker than an average human, and is covered in thick bristles.</description>
				<minSeverity>0.6</minSeverity>
				<statOffsets>
					<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.02</ArmorRating_Blunt>
					<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.03</ArmorRating_Sharp>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationStage">
				<minSeverity>0.8</minSeverity>
				<statOffsets>
					<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.02</ArmorRating_Blunt>
					<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.04</ArmorRating_Sharp>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</stages>
		<comps>
			<li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.CompProperties_MutationSeverityAdjust">
				<severityPerDay>0.33</severityPerDay>
			</li>
		</comps>
	</Pawnmorph.Hediffs.MutationDef>
</Defs>